Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.97,0:01:22.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这放秘方的保险柜也太耐用了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.97,0:01:22.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That secret formula safe is pretty durable
