Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.48,0:01:27.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe dynamite was the wrong choice
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.82,0:01:37.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,员工们  我得暂时远离痞老板一阵子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.82,0:01:37.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Crew, I need to get away from Plankton for a while
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.74,0:01:39.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我需要度个假
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.74,0:01:39.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I could use a vacation
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.32,0:01:41.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来场海上游轮之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.32,0:01:41.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A nice sea cruise
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.25,0:01:45.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坐游轮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.25,0:01:45.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A cruise
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.04,0:01:47.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,玩沙壶球
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.04,0:01:47.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The shuffleboard
