Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.67,0:01:51.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有晕船
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.67,0:01:51.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The sea sickness
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.50,0:01:53.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.50,0:01:53.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can--
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.34,0:01:54.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.34,0:01:54.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not we
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.67,0:01:55.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.67,0:01:55.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.17,0:01:56.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就我去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:01:56.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Alone
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.05,0:01:58.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住单人舱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.05,0:01:58.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cabin for one
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.30,0:02:01.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥先生  重建蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:01.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Squidward, rebuild the restaurant
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.97,0:02:03.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能干嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.97,0:02:03.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.43,0:02:05.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝我一路顺风
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.43,0:02:05.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wish me bon voy-ah-gee
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.94,0:02:09.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一路顺风
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.94,0:02:09.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bon voyage
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.40,0:02:10.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:10.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Goodbye
