Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.36,0:02:11.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Farewell
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.52,0:02:12.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,旅途愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.52,0:02:12.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy trails
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.61,0:02:15.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.61,0:02:15.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.03,0:02:16.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么你一定要走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.03,0:02:16.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why do you have to go?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.32,0:02:18.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经想死你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.32,0:02:18.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I miss you already
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.41,0:02:20.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别丢下我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:20.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't leave me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.20,0:02:26.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:26.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.04,0:02:27.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下就能去帮章鱼哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:27.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I get to help Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.13,0:02:33.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来我的客舱在楼下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:33.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like my cabin's downstairs
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.75,0:02:36.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  我先前是办伙食的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.75,0:02:36.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, I was the purveyor
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.43,0:02:44.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还得再下多少层啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.43,0:02:44.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How much further down do these decks go?
