Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.56,0:02:52.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,3
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.27,0:02:52.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,7
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.27,0:02:52.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,7
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.44,0:02:56.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:56.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here we go
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.24,0:03:02.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面比蜗牛壳还小
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:02.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's tighter than a snail's shell in here
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.16,0:03:04.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起码入住费还挺便宜的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:04.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But at least I got it cheap
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.29,0:03:09.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:09.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.37,0:03:10.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老痞子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.37,0:03:10.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.21,0:03:13.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:13.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.58,0:03:15.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还想远离你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.58,0:03:15.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm tryin' to get away from you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.71,0:03:17.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是我的客舱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:17.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is my cabin
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.09,0:03:19.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也还想远离你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.09,0:03:19.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I'm trying to get away from you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.47,0:03:21.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是我的客舱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.47,0:03:21.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is my cabin
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:24.85,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(852,810)}尤金蟹\N{\fnArial}237{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}号房\N双人入住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:24.85,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1634,900)}谢尔顿痞\N{\fnArial}237{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}号房\N双人入住
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.43,0:03:24.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,双人入住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:24.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Double occupancy"?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.18,0:03:32.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,整场游轮旅行都别让我看到听到你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.18,0:03:29.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I better not see you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.77,0:03:32.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I better not hear you for this whole cruise
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.69,0:03:34.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然海神王保佑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:34.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or so help me, Neptune
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.77,0:03:38.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到时我就把你的绿屁股丢到海里去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.77,0:03:38.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm tossin' your green keister overboard
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.19,0:03:40.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:40.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.24,0:03:43.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老子也会甩门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:43.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I can slam a hatch too, ya know
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:51.12,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(430,254)}果汁吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.96,0:03:57.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎旅客登船
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:57.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, ahoy there, passenger
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.42,0:04:01.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是鲁布  船上的活动负责人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:04:01.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Rube, the activities director on this ship
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.01,0:04:05.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要报名游玩我们狂野湿滑的水滑梯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:05.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I sign you up for our wet and wild waterslide?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.93,0:04:13.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太神了  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:13.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Amazing, isn't it?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.06,0:04:14.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉并不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:14.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't think
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.61,0:04:16.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.61,0:04:16.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.40,0:04:19.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,保证你会玩得特开心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:19.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're gonna have fun
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.23,0:04:21.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再找个伙伴配你一起滑就行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:21.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You just need a buddy to go down with
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.12,0:04:28.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说伙伴伙伴到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:28.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And here's your buddy now
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.24,0:04:29.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:29.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.79,0:04:30.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老痞子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:30.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.83,0:04:31.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:31.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.75,0:04:33.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来你们早认识了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:33.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You already know each other
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.92,0:04:35.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起锚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.92,0:04:35.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anchors aweigh
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.67,0:04:36.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:36.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.30,0:04:49.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说  伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:49.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say "Buddies"
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.40,0:05:05.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我非谴责你不可
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:05.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I rebuke you
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.78,0:05:07.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,离我远一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:07.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get away from me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.70,0:05:14.83,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 此为前面海绵所述的沙壶球 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.83,0:05:16.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶  宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:16.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, baby
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.21,0:05:17.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,十分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:17.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ten points
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.54,0:05:19.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板又赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:19.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton wins again
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.75,0:05:22.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自个儿玩就是不会输
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:22.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't lose when you play alone
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.01,0:05:27.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚远点  鲸鱼口粮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:27.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Buzz off, whale food
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.84,0:05:29.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这球场已经被我约走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:29.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm signed up for this court now
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.97,0:05:32.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咬藤壶去吧你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:32.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go bite a barnacle
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.01,0:05:33.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我预约的才对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.01,0:05:33.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm booked right now
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.14,0:05:35.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.14,0:05:35.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fish sticks
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.27,0:05:38.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不小心帮你们预约到了同一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:38.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I signed you both up for the same time
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.02,0:05:40.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望那样不成问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:40.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hope that won't be a prob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.19,0:05:43.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.19,0:05:43.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No prob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.11,0:05:44.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太神了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.11,0:05:44.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Amazing
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.50,0:05:57.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚开  傻壶螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.50,0:05:57.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shuffle off, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.80,0:06:10.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:10.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.64,0:06:53.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,船长说  铲煤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.64,0:06:53.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The captain says, "Shoveling coal
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.55,0:06:55.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你俩疯子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:55.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is what you two maniacs get
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.81,0:06:58.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在我船上闹事的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.81,0:06:58.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for causing trouble on my ship"
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.64,0:07:00.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝你们开心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.64,0:07:00.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So have fun, y'all
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.98,0:07:02.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真谢谢你了  谢尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:02.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot, Sheldon
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.98,0:07:05.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我假期都被你糟蹋了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.98,0:07:05.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You ruined my vacation
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.53,0:07:12.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全体成员
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:12.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All hands on deck
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.16,0:07:14.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,船失控了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:14.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've lost control of the ship
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.41,0:07:18.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海神王保佑  我们就快撞上冰山了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:18.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Neptune help us, we're headed straight for an iceberg
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:21.92,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1058,920)}冰 山
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.91,0:07:21.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就前边那个结球生菜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:21.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,lettuce, dead ahead
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.63,0:07:33.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不敢相信我居然会跟你一块儿独处
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:33.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I'm left here alone with just you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.51,0:07:38.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也不信我居然会跟你一块儿独处
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.51,0:07:38.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I can't believe I'm left here alone with just you too
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.02,0:07:40.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起码还有免费沙拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:40.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At least we have free salad
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.64,0:07:42.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:42.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boo
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.60,0:07:43.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚越远越好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.60,0:07:43.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good riddance
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.52,0:07:45.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我恨死你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:45.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hate you so
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.69,0:07:48.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可不可以丢点千岛酱下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:48.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can ya throw down some Thousand Island dressing?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.82,0:07:52.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两位好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:52.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ahoy there, you two
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.33,0:07:59.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁要来做救生艇演练啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.33,0:07:59.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now who's up for a lifeboat drill?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.96,0:08:05.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  下次再说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:05.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, maybe next time
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.13,0:08:09.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水好冷啊  冷到我腿都麻了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:09.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The water's so cold I can barely feel my legs
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.84,0:08:11.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太神了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:11.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ah-mayyy-zing
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.93,0:08:15.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  开始划船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.93,0:08:15.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's start paddling
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.80,0:08:17.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你划错方向了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:17.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're going the wrong way
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.14,0:08:18.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  划这方向
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:18.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, this way
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.18,0:08:19.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:19.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.06,0:08:20.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,划这方向
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:20.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This way
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.23,0:08:22.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正确的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:22.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The right way
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.73,0:08:25.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,第二天
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.61,0:08:33.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这方向才是正确的方向吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:33.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This way is the right way, eh?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.11,0:08:34.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,划这方向就被困住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:34.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, this way we're stranded
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.87,0:08:39.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你脚踩到我这半边的荒岛来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.87,0:08:39.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your foot is on my side of the deserted island
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.20,0:08:41.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还不是你老乱改界线
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.20,0:08:41.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you keep moving the line
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.91,0:08:45.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个在这啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.91,0:08:45.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you two are
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.63,0:08:49.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我到处都在找你们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:49.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been looking for you all over
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.09,0:08:53.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我帮你俩都报了名  一起到沙滩骑行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.09,0:08:53.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got you both signed up for a bike ride on the beach
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.84,0:08:56.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是给你量身定制的活动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.84,0:08:56.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's an activity for you
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.81,0:09:01.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,投得挺准
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.81,0:09:01.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice throw
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.89,0:09:02.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:02.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.89,0:09:04.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打气筒给我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.89,0:09:04.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hand me that bicycle pump
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.85,0:09:05.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:05.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.90,0:09:08.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要骑着橡胶裤离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.90,0:09:08.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna ride ol' rubber pants outta here
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.57,0:09:13.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别丢下我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:13.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not without me
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.83,0:09:21.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.83,0:09:21.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.29,0:09:24.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我肚子好胀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.29,0:09:24.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm all bloated
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.46,0:09:26.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好解开一下腰带
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:26.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Better undo my belt
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.00,0:09:27.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:27.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.17,0:09:27.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.17,0:09:27.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.00,0:09:31.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太神了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:31.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ah-may-ziiiing
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.42,0:09:38.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脚趾头好凉快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:38.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That is brisk on the little piggies
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.27,0:09:46.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有宝藏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:46.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Treasure
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.61,0:09:51.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:51.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.86,0:09:53.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:53.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.11,0:09:54.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:54.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.53,0:09:58.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我向来都会来酷乐湖寻宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:58.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I always come to Goo Lagoon to look for treasure
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.41,0:10:00.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有一次我找到了个瓶盖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:10:00.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Once I found a bottle cap
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.54,0:10:04.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,酷乐湖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.54,0:10:04.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Goo Lagoon?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.34,0:10:16.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你之前还说那些声音是幻听
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:16.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You said all those sounds were hallucinations
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.47,0:10:19.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还不是你膝盖不中用  不肯逛岛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.47,0:10:18.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you wouldn't explore the island
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:19.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because of your knees
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.09,0:10:21.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.09,0:10:21.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.05,0:10:23.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下我真得要来趟假期远离你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.05,0:10:23.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I really need a vacation from you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.60,0:10:26.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还更得要来趟假期远离你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:26.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not as much as I need one from you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.18,0:10:28.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,一周后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:29.10,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(366,372)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:30.69,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(366,372)}蟹堡工
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.45,0:10:41.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这边最近真是安静得很
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:41.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure has been quiet around here
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.20,0:10:44.54,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(704,770)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.04,0:10:47.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这边最近真是无聊得很
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:47.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It sure has been boring around here
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.58,0:10:50.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:50.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yello
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.33,0:10:52.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.33,0:10:52.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.25,0:10:53.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老痞子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:53.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.84,0:10:56.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你背后藏了什么  尤金
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:56.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What'cha got there behind your back, Eugene?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.09,0:10:58.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.09,0:10:58.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I just thought
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.34,0:11:00.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是  你应该会比较想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:11:00.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ya know, you might wanna
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.34,0:11:01.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.34,0:11:01.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,maybe
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.26,0:11:04.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来试试看  就那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:04.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,take a crack at, uh, ya know
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.51,0:11:06.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,偷我秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:06.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,stealing me formuler?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.40,0:11:13.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿来吧你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:13.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gimme that
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.99,0:11:24.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它干嘛跑这边来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:24.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is this doing here?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.62,0:11:32.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,平平安安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:32.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Safe and sound
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.25,0:11:38.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.25,0:11:38.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ahoy there, you two
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.67,0:11:43.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来咱都报名来这参加转瓶子游戏了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.67,0:11:41.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like we're all signed up in here
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.01,0:11:43.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for a game of Spin The Bottle
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.60,0:11:47.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太神了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:47.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ah-maaayyy-zing
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:52.02,画面,,0,0,0,,{\i1}类星体船长 下一代
