Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.95,0:12:05.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,类星体船长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:05.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Captain Quasar
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.99,0:12:08.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:08.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Save me
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.25,0:12:14.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把派大机放了  鸡嘴哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.25,0:12:14.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You let Pat-Tron go, Chicken Man
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.40,0:12:39.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海神王啊  你身后那啥东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.40,0:12:39.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sweet Neptune, what's that behind you?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.91,0:12:49.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.91,0:12:49.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My hero
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.74,0:12:52.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.74,0:12:52.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You saved me
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.04,0:12:53.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那当然了  派大机
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.04,0:12:53.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course, Pat-Tron
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.46,0:12:57.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁都不许欺负类星体船长的船员
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:57.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nobody messes with Captain Quasar's crew
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.26,0:13:06.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这集真好看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.26,0:13:06.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What an episode
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.64,0:13:07.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打斗真精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:07.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a battle
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.18,0:13:10.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,类星体船长再次大获成功
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:10.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Captain Quasar does it again
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.68,0:13:12.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这集拥抱的戏我都喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.68,0:13:12.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I liked all the hugging
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.89,0:13:18.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们说外面不会真的有鸡嘴哥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.89,0:13:16.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guys, you don't suppose
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:18.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,there's real Chicken Men out there, do you?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.36,0:13:20.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然没有了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:20.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course not, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.98,0:13:23.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是做电视节目虚构出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.98,0:13:23.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're just made up for TV
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.03,0:13:25.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就像动画片  或者法国
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:25.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,like cartoons, or France
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.37,0:13:33.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,呼唤全体类星体船长粉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:33.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,, Calling all Captain Quasar fans
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.50,0:13:38.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,速来类星体船长粉丝俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:35.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your presence is required
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:38.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,at the only Captain Quasar fan club
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.29,0:13:40.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三海地区独家限定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:40.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in the tri-ocean area
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:40.54,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1004,646)}裤头村
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.55,0:13:46.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快快传送到我们总部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:46.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Beam over to our headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.38,0:13:48.30,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(950,226)}超棒漫画店
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.38,0:13:48.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,地址就在漫画店后面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.38,0:13:48.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in the back of the comic book shop
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.43,0:13:54.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一场会议日期是太空日76359-1
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.43,0:13:54.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The next meeting is on space-date 76359-1
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.48,0:13:58.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(932.727,837.273)}旧月
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.19,0:13:57.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是今天  你们几位太空学员
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.19,0:13:57.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's today, ya space cadets
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.19,0:14:02.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要加入粉丝俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:02.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We gotta join that fan club
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.57,0:14:07.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:07.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:11.41,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1641.818,495.454)}仅限硬核\N类星体粉丝
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.49,0:14:11.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,换油半价
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.49,0:14:11.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Half Price Oil Change"
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.41,0:14:14.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:14.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.70,0:14:18.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上面写的是  仅限硬核类星体粉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:18.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it says, "Hardcore Quasar Fans Only"
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.62,0:14:20.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可硬汉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:20.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm hard-boiled
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.42,0:14:21.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:21.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, guys
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.88,0:14:27.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.88,0:14:27.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Greetings
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.09,0:14:31.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临类星体船长官方粉丝俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.09,0:14:31.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Official Captain Quasar Fan Club
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.72,0:14:35.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我海霸王  很明显就是部长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.72,0:14:35.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I, Bubble Bass, am president, obviously
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.81,0:14:38.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哈维跟凯文是联合秘书
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.81,0:14:38.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Harvey and Kevin are co-secretaries
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.56,0:14:44.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们一直都在寻找新成员
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:44.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We are always on the lookout for new members
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.44,0:14:49.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然而  依你们破破烂烂的皮套来看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:49.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,However, judging by your rather shabby cosplay
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.61,0:14:54.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,估计你们都是旧版类星体剧粉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.61,0:14:54.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I surmise you are fans of the original Quasar series
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.41,0:14:57.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这家粉丝俱乐部只粉重启版
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:57.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This fan club is only for the reboot
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.96,0:15:02.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,类星体船长  下一代
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.96,0:15:02.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Captain Quasar: The Next Iteration
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.30,0:15:08.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以类星体船长做了新版的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:08.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They made a new Captain Quasar show?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.26,0:15:10.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:10.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Indeed
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.72,0:15:13.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且新版好看不少
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:13.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And it is the far superior series
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.72,0:15:17.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因此  这些你们用不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:17.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Therefore, you won't be needing any of this
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.31,0:15:21.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会议开头呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.31,0:15:21.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, to begin our meeting
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.65,0:15:24.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先来看一段新版片段吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:24.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,let's watch a clip from the new show
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.29,0:15:47.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大机  启动阿尔法式机甲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:47.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pat-Tron, activate Mecha Pattern Alpha
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.36,0:16:13.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.36,0:16:13.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dinner is served
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.32,0:16:16.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以等下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:16.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.37,0:16:19.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,类星体船长现在变机甲片了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:19.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,now Captain Quasar is a giant robot show?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.75,0:16:22.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,主题应该是探索宇宙才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:22.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought it was about exploring the universe
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.83,0:16:24.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以两者兼得
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.83,0:16:24.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It can be both
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.04,0:16:25.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:25.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.79,0:16:27.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那样基本设定就乱套了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:27.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It confuses the premise
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.34,0:16:28.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我支持鱿鱼妹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:28.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm with Squidina
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.55,0:16:31.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,旧版类星体  好看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:31.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Original Quasar, yay
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:30.80,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(741.819,186.363)}类星体
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.88,0:16:34.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,重启版类星体  不好看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.88,0:16:34.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Reboot Quasar, nay
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.13,0:16:33.30,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1610.909,330)}新类星体
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.72,0:16:36.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我喜欢新版
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.72,0:16:36.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I like the new one
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.80,0:16:39.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这机器人可帅了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:39.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The robot is so handsome
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.43,0:16:40.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:40.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fine
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.56,0:16:42.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,俱乐部就你们办去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:42.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You guys can have your club
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.52,0:16:44.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要办自己的俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:44.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're gonna start our own
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.44,0:16:47.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,专门粉旧版
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:47.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to celebrate the original series
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.15,0:16:48.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吧  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.15,0:16:48.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.32,0:16:52.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.32,0:16:52.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh boy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.53,0:16:55.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能开新俱乐部真是超级激动  鱿鱼妹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:55.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm super excited for our new club, Squidina
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.49,0:16:56.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:56.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.20,0:16:57.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,俱乐部会议要上哪开呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:16:57.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,where are we having the meeting?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.74,0:16:59.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是可以在你家开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.74,0:16:59.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought we could do it at your place?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.12,0:17:00.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然我很乐意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.12,0:17:00.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd love to
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.95,0:17:03.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但小蜗已经说好要征用我家了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.95,0:17:03.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but Gary said he needed the house to himself today
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.80,0:17:13.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道可以去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:13.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know a place we can go
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.38,0:17:14.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:14.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Follow me
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.47,0:17:22.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这地方有点挤啊  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:22.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This place is a little tight, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.39,0:17:23.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.39,0:17:23.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,True
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.10,0:17:24.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是有零食吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.10,0:17:24.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But it comes with snacks
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.27,0:17:27.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来开会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:27.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's start our meeting
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.85,0:17:31.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先做类星体船长秘密俱乐部握手式
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.85,0:17:31.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with the Captain Quasar secret club handshake
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.40,0:17:33.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,类星体学员  发射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:33.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quasar Cadets, blast off
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.44,0:17:36.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.44,0:17:36.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.28,0:17:38.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该要发射才对的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.28,0:17:38.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're supposed to blast off
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.70,0:17:41.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经尽力在发射了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.70,0:17:41.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm blasting off as hard as I can
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.12,0:17:47.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我薯片被个黄色玩意给卡住了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.12,0:17:47.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My chips are caught on some yellow thing
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.58,0:17:51.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再买一袋呗  把你原先那袋顶出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:51.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Buy another bag, it'll knock your chips loose
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.22,0:18:00.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来必须得使出
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:18:00.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like I'll have to give it the old
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.43,0:18:02.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新版类星体摇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.43,0:18:02.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,new Quasar shake
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.64,0:18:07.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.64,0:18:07.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Huzzah
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.85,0:18:09.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免费零食
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.85,0:18:09.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Free snacks
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.48,0:18:13.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,类星体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:13.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quasar
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.03,0:18:20.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想吐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.03,0:18:20.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Queasy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.20,0:18:25.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能想到的地方全都试过了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:25.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, we tried the only place I could think of
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.95,0:18:28.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来也没得选了  只能重新加入
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.95,0:18:28.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like we have no choice but to rejoin
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.83,0:18:32.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们的破烂新版类星体船长俱乐部了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:32.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,their dumb old new Captain Quasar club
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.63,0:18:40.14,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1505.455,880.909)}类星体船长\N今日签名
Dialogue: 1,0:18:36.76,0:18:40.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,居然还找了新类星体船长来签名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:40.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They got the new Captain Quasar to sign autographs?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.14,0:18:41.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.14,0:18:41.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Impressive
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.60,0:18:44.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不得不承认  确实不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.60,0:18:44.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hate to admit it, but it is impressive
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.14,0:18:48.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且还让我想到办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.14,0:18:48.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and it gives me an idea
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.02,0:18:53.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是你的头号粉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.02,0:18:53.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm your biggest fan
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.44,0:18:55.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  我才是你的头号粉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.44,0:18:55.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I'm your biggest fan
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.61,0:18:57.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能做我爹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.61,0:18:57.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will you be my daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.94,0:18:57.36,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1101.818,179.091)}爹
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.36,0:18:58.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好  艾迪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.36,0:18:58.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen, Eddie
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.32,0:19:01.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早跟你说过别再办签名会了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.32,0:19:01.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I told you, no more autograph shows
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.66,0:19:04.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可是演员  不是书法家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:04.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm an actor, not a calligrapher
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.74,0:19:09.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看是谁爬回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:09.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, look who's come crawling back
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.75,0:19:11.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好承认
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.75,0:19:11.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready to admit that
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.04,0:19:14.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,类星体船长下一代
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.04,0:19:14.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Captain Quasar: The Next Iteration
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.04,0:19:16.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是最棒的一代了没
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:16.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is the best iteration?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.01,0:19:18.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,休想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:18.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.05,0:19:22.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那凭什么要来我们盛大的明星签名会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:22.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then why did you come to our big celebrity signing?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.64,0:19:27.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要把你介绍给几位老朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:27.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We wanted to introduce you to some old friends
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.64,0:19:32.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们把我们带到了什么奇异新世界来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.64,0:19:32.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What strange new world have you brought us to?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.11,0:19:37.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,旧版派大机跟类星体船长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.11,0:19:37.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The old-school Pat-Tron and Captain Quasar?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.53,0:19:40.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们到底上哪找来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.53,0:19:40.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where on Earth did you find them?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.24,0:19:42.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没到地底  是到外太空
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:42.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not on Earth, in outer space
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.86,0:19:45.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们飞船的坐标代码
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.86,0:19:45.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I still had their ship's coordinates
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.03,0:19:47.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还在派大星的旧时旅柜上面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:47.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,programmed into Patrick's old time closet
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.62,0:19:48.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:48.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My what now?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.79,0:19:50.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的时旅柜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:50.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your time closet
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.50,0:19:55.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以让你抵达一切时空
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:55.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It gives you access to all of time and space?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.67,0:19:59.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完全没印象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:19:59.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Doesn't ring a bell
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.88,0:20:02.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是装你房间里那个  就在爸妈家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.88,0:20:02.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was in your room, at Mom and Dad's house?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.68,0:20:03.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想起来没
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:03.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Remember?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.64,0:20:06.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:06.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.06,0:20:08.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.06,0:20:08.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I remember
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.68,0:20:11.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁是爸妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:11.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who are "Mom" and "Dad"?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.02,0:20:11.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总之
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:11.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anyhow
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.06,0:20:16.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然俩类星体跟俩派大机都到齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:16.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,now that we've got both Quasars and both Pat-Trons here
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.36,0:20:19.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就让他们合作拍部新剧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.36,0:20:19.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,let's team 'em up for a new series
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.40,0:20:22.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想想他们会展开怎样的精彩冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.40,0:20:22.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just think of the exciting adventures they could have
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.49,0:20:24.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们可以一起烤蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:24.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They could bake a cake together
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.61,0:20:26.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者拼拼图
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.61,0:20:26.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or solve a jigsaw puzzle
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.37,0:20:28.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者坐在火边静静地看书
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:28.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or read quietly by the fire
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.66,0:20:31.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听着可真精彩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.66,0:20:31.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That does sound exciting
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.04,0:20:37.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然还是确认哪个类星体最强好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:37.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or instead, let's find out who the best Quasar is
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.96,0:20:40.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,直接速战速决
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:40.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,once and for all
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.97,0:20:50.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就让他们在末日无底洞里面决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:50.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,by having them fight it out in the Pit of Doom
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.85,0:20:53.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这地方为什么会有末日无底洞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.85,0:20:53.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why does this place have a pit of doom?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.23,0:20:54.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那还用问
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:54.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Duh
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.35,0:20:57.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每家漫画店都有个末日无底洞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:57.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Every comic book store has a pit of doom
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.19,0:20:58.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,合情合理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.19,0:20:58.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That makes sense
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.52,0:21:00.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,类星体船长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.52,0:21:00.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Captain Quasar
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.40,0:21:03.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们跟我们长得好像
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.40,0:21:03.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those guys look exactly like us
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.49,0:21:05.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,难道他们是克隆体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.49,0:21:05.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are they clones?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.61,0:21:07.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别傻了  派大机
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.61,0:21:07.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly, Pat-Tron
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.78,0:21:10.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是跟我们长得有几分像而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.78,0:21:10.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They only kind of look like us
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.12,0:21:11.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以他们就是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:11.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That makes them
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.16,0:21:13.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邪恶克隆体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.16,0:21:13.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,evil clones
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.25,0:21:17.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟克隆我一次算你狠那集一个样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:17.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just like in "Clone Me Once, Shame on You"
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.79,0:21:19.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱看那集
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.79,0:21:19.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love that episode
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.50,0:21:21.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大机  进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,0:21:21.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pat-Tron, attack
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.88,0:21:24.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别打脸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:24.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not the face
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.10,0:21:36.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来我的类星体要赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.10,0:21:36.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, looks like my Quasar is winning
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.10,0:21:39.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要抢先一步幸灾乐祸了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.10,0:21:39.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll begin gloating now to get a head start
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.95,0:21:47.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些克隆体太强了  船长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.95,0:21:47.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These clones are too strong, Captain
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.95,0:21:49.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说得确实  派大机
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.95,0:21:49.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You may be right, Pat-Tron
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.66,0:21:52.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该使出激光了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.66,0:21:52.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to use our lasers
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.24,0:21:53.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:53.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.33,0:21:55.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们真有激光吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.33,0:21:55.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You guys have real lasers?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.05,0:22:03.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胜利了  派大机
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.05,0:22:03.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Victory, Pat-Tron
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.76,0:22:06.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们的邪恶克隆体脸都丢尽了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.76,0:22:06.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our evil clones are humiliated
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.88,0:22:08.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.88,0:22:08.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.73,0:22:16.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:16.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.77,0:22:17.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,算你赢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.77,0:22:17.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You win
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.89,0:22:21.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我特此宣布本类星体船长俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.89,0:22:21.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hereby declare this Captain Quasar club
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.36,0:22:25.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,向各代粉丝开放
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.36,0:22:25.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,open to fans of all iterations
Dialogue: 1,0:22:29.24,0:22:31.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的天啊  船长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.24,0:22:31.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Holy mackerel, Captain
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.66,0:22:34.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是邪恶克隆体大军
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.66,0:22:34.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,An army of evil clones
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.58,0:22:36.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它们一定是在增殖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.58,0:22:36.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They must be multiplying
Dialogue: 1,0:22:36.54,0:22:38.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快行动  免得它们又分裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.54,0:22:38.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurry, before they can split again
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.46,0:22:43.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就好像克隆我两次算我笨那集
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.46,0:22:43.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just like in the episode "Clone Me Twice, Shame on Me"
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.76,0:22:48.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,史上最棒粉丝俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.76,0:22:48.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Best fan club ever
